Package: ParetoGrilli
Title: Runs Pareto Analysis tools from Zwijnenburg, Grilli & Engelbrecht (2022)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Grilli", , "joseph.grilli@oecd.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-5857-5568"))
Description: This package contains the codes necessary to replicate the pareto analysis in Zwijnenburg, Grilli & Engelbrecht (2022). It also allows users to estimate pareto (type 1 and generalized) functions in the presence of top-end truncation, and generate samples from partially covered pareto distributions.
